<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="18300000t" end="37500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂？战场原</font></p>
<p begin="40400000t" end="99600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么了？这个时候给我打电话  是说这次的麻烦已经解决了么？</font></p>
<p begin="108400000t" end="125500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还没弄完</font></p>
<p begin="135900000t" end="159700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">抱歉  是我没忍住</font></p>
<p begin="162190000t" end="173500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">感觉有些心慌</font></p>
<p begin="176400000t" end="182200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="186400000t" end="217300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也罢  羽川同学的事情就交给我就好了</font></p>
<p begin="219800000t" end="243500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？羽川她遇到什么事了么？</font></p>
<p begin="250200000t" end="267300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">神原没和你说吗？</font></p>
<p begin="277300000t" end="284000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说什么？</font></p>
<p begin="288600000t" end="338600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">算了  既然没和你说  那你就回来之后直接问她本人好了</font></p>
<p begin="367000000t" end="383700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说  战场原</font></p>
<p begin="389900000t" end="412000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我有件事想问你</font></p>
<p begin="419100000t" end="470400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一年前  神原到直江津高中入学  过来见你的时候</font></p>
<p begin="473300000t" end="493800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老实说  你当时是什么想法？</font></p>
<p begin="498400000t" end="548800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个嘛  老实说  我当时觉得她的感情对我来说太沉重了</font></p>
<p begin="567200000t" end="620200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而无法承受她的「重」  这或许也也表现出了我的「轻」</font></p>
<p begin="636400000t" end="693600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果我想要和神原在一起  就必须让自己能够承受她的重量</font></p>
<p begin="701900000t" end="729800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事到如今我还在钻研</font></p>
<p begin="736900000t" end="757000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">别看我这样  我也是一直在努力的</font></p>
<p begin="762800000t" end="789100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为了能当上阿良良木同学的新娘</font></p>
<p begin="806000000t" end="812600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是不是太沉重了？</font></p>
<p begin="817400000t" end="839100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  一点也不沉重</font></p>
<p begin="908800000t" end="955500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这可能是最后的机会了  我可以问一件可能会让你生气的事吗？</font></p>
<p begin="979700000t" end="1026400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果有比我条件更好的人向你表白  到时候你会怎么办？</font></p>
<p begin="1050200000t" end="1078900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我百分之百会变心</font></p>
<p begin="1086900000t" end="1106100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你可真不一般</font></p>
<p begin="1111900000t" end="1131500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">能说出这种话真是不一般</font></p>
<p begin="1139800000t" end="1173600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为我知道世上没有绝不会断的羁绊</font></p>
<p begin="1191400000t" end="1214300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我看到自己的父母就明白了</font></p>
<p begin="1218700000t" end="1240800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原  那个…这…</font></p>
<p begin="1244100000t" end="1280800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">绝不会断的羁绊  仔细想来其实是很可怕的</font></p>
<p begin="1287100000t" end="1331700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以为了不让我变心  你也应该要努力才对</font></p>
<p begin="1337500000t" end="1377200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算无法成为一个特别的人  但你也可以成为某人眼里特别的人</font></p>
<p begin="1392600000t" end="1413000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">某人眼里…特别的人</font></p>
<p begin="1417800000t" end="1473300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我为了成为神原和阿良良木同学眼里特别的人  从未停止过努力</font></p>
<p begin="1481800000t" end="1528100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">放心吧  阿良良木同学  你已经足够是一个特别的人了</font></p>
<p begin="1534400000t" end="1560300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">无论是在我眼里  还是在神原眼里</font></p>
<p begin="1564000000t" end="1578200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也包括在小忍的眼里</font></p>
<p begin="1584900000t" end="1604500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是我们选择了你</font></p>
<p begin="1614500000t" end="1648700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你还真够了解我的  真不一般</font></p>
<p begin="1652200000t" end="1664300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁让我是你女朋友呢？</font></p>
<p begin="1671000000t" end="1698500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">能接到你的电话  我非常开心</font></p>
<p begin="1709000000t" end="1717500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我爱你</font></p>
<p begin="1727100000t" end="1735000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我也爱你</font></p>
<p begin="1748400000t" end="1788800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">等我回来以后  我们再多聊聊这些话题吧</font></p>
<p begin="1796100000t" end="1816600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  我全裸待机</font></p>
<p begin="1838900000t" end="1875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">神原的变态属性  肯定是受到你的强烈影响</font></p>
<p begin="2498400000t" end="2528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="32">{\an8}忍与盔甲  其六</font></p>
<p begin="2655000000t" end="2681300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那咱们就赶紧开始赶紧结束吧</font></p>
<p begin="2688800000t" end="2693800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">过来</font></p>
<p begin="2755500000t" end="2773100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了  这样就行了</font></p>
<p begin="2793100000t" end="2833100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">准备完毕  现在阿良良木同学也已经是临战态势了</font></p>
<p begin="2839800000t" end="2872700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">准备完毕？这也叫准备完毕？</font></p>
<p begin="2878200000t" end="2932000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂  稍等片刻  汝的连接怎么办？阿良良木阁下</font></p>
<p begin="2936600000t" end="2986200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">汝该不会是想要以如此弱小的状态与在下决斗吧</font></p>
<p begin="2994300000t" end="3003500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}他的声音，已经不是从我这里夺取的声音</font></p>
<p begin="3003500000t" end="3012300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}而是恢复成了他自己的</font></p>
<p begin="3014500000t" end="3022100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎呀哎呀</font></p>
<p begin="3030000000t" end="3090500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看来汝与姬丝秀忒之间的羁绊也没有在下担心的那么深嘛</font></p>
<p begin="3097100000t" end="3147600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">竟然把自己的仆从以如此弱小的状态送上战场  简直难以置信</font></p>
<p begin="3167600000t" end="3196400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我并不想借小忍的力量取得胜利</font></p>
<p begin="3199700000t" end="3226400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是想取得胜利  并成为小忍的力量</font></p>
<p begin="3236900000t" end="3248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">算了  这样也好</font></p>
<p begin="3260200000t" end="3330700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过伊豆湖阁下  请您在决斗规则上多给他一些机会好了</font></p>
<p begin="3334900000t" end="3358200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">免得他找一些难堪的借口</font></p>
<p begin="3362800000t" end="3421600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那是当然  我打算采用一个自古以来广为人知的普遍规则</font></p>
<p begin="3427000000t" end="3460000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是为了在一定程度上让你们公平竞争</font></p>
<p begin="3547600000t" end="3580100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就叫它「假想·妖刀心渡」好了</font></p>
<p begin="3587600000t" end="3605600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">里面当然是注有灵气的</font></p>
<p begin="3610600000t" end="3653100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个嘛  你们就当这是对双方都有效的电击枪好了</font></p>
<p begin="3661000000t" end="3705200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">首先  你们两个要背对背地站在这把竹刀的两侧</font></p>
<p begin="3710700000t" end="3759900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后随着我的计数  各自向前方走十步</font></p>
<p begin="3764500000t" end="3789900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">走完这十步之后  决斗便随即开始</font></p>
<p begin="3795300000t" end="3833300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">先到达这把竹刀旁边并给对方一击的就算获胜</font></p>
<p begin="3839500000t" end="3874200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然  从对方手中抢走竹刀并给予反击也是被允许的</font></p>
<p begin="3876200000t" end="3903400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">决斗的基准便是「一刀定胜负」</font></p>
<p begin="3914200000t" end="3925900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简单说来</font></p>
<p begin="3930900000t" end="3954700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这与其说是追求公平</font></p>
<p begin="3959700000t" end="4008900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不如说是为了让阿良良木阁下能在决斗中保住性命</font></p>
<p begin="4013500000t" end="4033500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是煞费苦心</font></p>
<p begin="4038500000t" end="4051400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还有什么问题？</font></p>
<p begin="4056000000t" end="4062700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没有</font></p>
<p begin="4066800000t" end="4081900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学有什么问题吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4086000000t" end="4109800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">无论是剑术还是战斗我都是外行</font></p>
<p begin="4109800000t" end="4154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这仅剩的十步距离的短跑方面  我可以先请教一下专家吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4158600000t" end="4170100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">专家？</font></p>
<p begin="4198600000t" end="4207800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">OK</font></p>
<p begin="4211200000t" end="4234900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">再加上这些让先应该也无所谓</font></p>
<p begin="4244500000t" end="4263700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">现在是七点半</font></p>
<p begin="4272100000t" end="4292500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们就在八点整开始决斗吧</font></p>
<p begin="4297100000t" end="4332900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">双方选手请做好热身运动</font></p>
<p begin="4356700000t" end="4405100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从身高来推测  阿良良木学长的步幅大约为72公分</font></p>
<p begin="4409700000t" end="4445600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因此十步的距离  就是7米零20公分</font></p>
<p begin="4452600000t" end="4507300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正如马拉松有马拉松的战略  百米冲刺有百米冲刺的战略</font></p>
<p begin="4510600000t" end="4546900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">七米冲刺也有七米冲刺的战略</font></p>
<p begin="4553600000t" end="4585300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过在目前的情况下  如何留有余力或许才是问题所在</font></p>
<p begin="4591100000t" end="4601100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么问题？</font></p>
<p begin="4606600000t" end="4634900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">决斗并不是跑完就结束</font></p>
<p begin="4640300000t" end="4675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你们还要抓起竹刀并给予对方一击呢</font></p>
<p begin="4677500000t" end="4691600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  也对</font></p>
