<p begin="8428100000t" end="8439300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">二</font></p>
<p begin="8443500000t" end="8451000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}三</font></p>
<p begin="8445200000t" end="8458500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">三</font></p>
<p begin="8461000000t" end="8469000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}四</font></p>
<p begin="8463100000t" end="8475200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">四</font></p>
<p begin="8478500000t" end="8486100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}五</font></p>
<p begin="8480200000t" end="8489400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">五</font></p>
<p begin="8496100000t" end="8504000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}六</font></p>
<p begin="8497700000t" end="8507300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">六</font></p>
<p begin="8513600000t" end="8521500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}七</font></p>
<p begin="8514400000t" end="8526100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">七</font></p>
<p begin="8531100000t" end="8539000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}八</font></p>
<p begin="8531900000t" end="8544400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">八</font></p>
<p begin="8549000000t" end="8556100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}九</font></p>
<p begin="8549900000t" end="8561100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">九</font></p>
<p begin="8569500000t" end="8575700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">十</font></p>
<p begin="9046000000t" end="9069800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是爻的…啊  原来是这样</font></p>
<p begin="9101500000t" end="9129400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是令人吃惊  这我还真没想过</font></p>
<p begin="9134400000t" end="9200300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">居然把我「给对方一击」的规则曲解成「给对方一次触击」</font></p>
<p begin="9276800000t" end="9304000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬…姬丝秀忒</font></p>
<p begin="9307700000t" end="9316500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒</font></p>
<p begin="9320600000t" end="9330200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀…</font></p>
<p begin="9562100000t" end="9575100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒…</font></p>
<p begin="9585500000t" end="9595900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒…</font></p>
<p begin="9605900000t" end="9620900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒…</font></p>
<p begin="9631400000t" end="9643900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀…</font></p>
<p begin="9679700000t" end="9709400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然我不知道自己能活到几岁</font></p>
<p begin="9715600000t" end="9736900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果能在有生之年再见一面的话</font></p>
<p begin="9749800000t" end="9761500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果能再见一面的话</font></p>
<p begin="9769800000t" end="9779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那就再见吧</font></p>
<p begin="9888300000t" end="9914100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不必道歉  吾已经原谅汝了</font></p>
<p begin="10026300000t" end="10045900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是吾不对</font></p>
<p begin="10106000000t" end="10116900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">生死郎</font></p>
<p begin="10207800000t" end="10260690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}能再见到汝真是高兴  吾还以为再也见不到汝了</font></p>
<p begin="10282000000t" end="10304100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}但是  吾等再也不会相见了</font></p>
<p begin="10350000000t" end="10388000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如今的吾  已经有了比汝更重要的人</font></p>
<p begin="10392500000t" end="10427200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吾暂时想要为了他而存在</font></p>
<p begin="10475990000t" end="10534400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">即不痛快  也算不上畅快  说出来也并没有因此而感到轻松</font></p>
<p begin="10540200000t" end="10554800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这样无可救赎</font></p>
<p begin="10566900000t" end="10609800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而  即使这样  自执行的时日起经过了四百年</font></p>
<p begin="10638200000t" end="10669900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他终于自杀成功了</font></p>
<p begin="10707200000t" end="10748500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好好  那么在那之后又怎么样了？  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="10753100000t" end="10775600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">后日谈还有这次的结局呢？</font></p>
<p begin="10779400000t" end="10809400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那之后就和我之前讲过的一样</font></p>
<p begin="10813200000t" end="10872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我和先到我家的神原会合  为了羽川的老虎一事而会合</font></p>
<p begin="10877000000t" end="10926200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后我就赶到了羽川身边  神原则赶到了战场原那里</font></p>
<p begin="10930400000t" end="10958300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  这样啊这样啊</font></p>
<p begin="10960400000t" end="10991700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">呀  真是谢谢你  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="10997500000t" end="11025900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样一来拼图就全部填好了</font></p>
<p begin="11036700000t" end="11078000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这和之前讲过的故事在某些细节上似乎还有一些矛盾</font></p>
<p begin="11081800000t" end="11154300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">弄清这些矛盾也正是所有故事的听者  也就是我忍野扇的乐趣</font></p>
<p begin="11156200000t" end="11169200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}历专家</font></p>
<p begin="11184000000t" end="11206100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">今无是3月13日</font></p>
<p begin="11211100000t" end="11241100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是我升学考试当天的早晨</font></p>
<p begin="11248600000t" end="11267400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我今天就先回去了</font></p>
<p begin="11270700000t" end="11289100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果还有有生之年的话就再见吧</font></p>
<p begin="11296600000t" end="11304500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还有一点</font></p>
<p begin="11311200000t" end="11351200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍小姐究竟有没有把第一个眷属吃干净呢？</font></p>
<p begin="11354500000t" end="11380000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？这个…我不是说过吃干净了吗？</font></p>
<p begin="11382500000t" end="11394200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一点也没剩？</font></p>
<p begin="11395800000t" end="11411700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  一点没剩</font></p>
<p begin="11415400000t" end="11422100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">连盔甲一起？</font></p>
<p begin="11427300000t" end="11431100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎！</font></p>
<p begin="11451300000t" end="11471700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该也吃了吧…</font></p>
<p begin="11474200000t" end="11486800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可能吃了</font></p>
<p begin="11496800000t" end="11503000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是…</font></p>
<p begin="11525100000t" end="11547200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这有那么重要吗？</font></p>
<p begin="11549700000t" end="11605600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为那副盔甲也是初代怪异杀手的血肉  同时也是他的筋骨</font></p>
<p begin="11608100000t" end="11690700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以如果把那副盔甲焙掉之后再加以锻造  应该还可以再造一把吧</font></p>
<p begin="11693600000t" end="11707400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">造一把妖刀心渡</font></p>
<p begin="11713400000t" end="11745400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果运气好的话  或许还能造一把小太刀梦渡</font></p>
<p begin="11750800000t" end="11761200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">梦渡？</font></p>
<p begin="11767500000t" end="11822100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果我是卧烟小姐的话  肯定会在忍小姐吃掉盔甲之前将其回收</font></p>
<p begin="11827900000t" end="11867100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定艾比索特就是因为这件事才被叫过来的</font></p>
<p begin="11873800000t" end="11899300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">卧烟小姐役有道理会做这种事吧</font></p>
<p begin="11903800000t" end="11938500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我倒是觉得小忍应该是连盔甲也一起吃掉了</font></p>
<p begin="11942200000t" end="11964300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  应该就是这么一回事</font></p>
<p begin="11977700000t" end="12029000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那接下来我也回答阿良良木学长一个疑问好了</font></p>
<p begin="12030600000t" end="12045700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？我的疑问？</font></p>
<p begin="12051100000t" end="12065700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我有什么疑问？</font></p>
<p begin="12069800000t" end="12083200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">死尸累生死郎</font></p>
<p begin="12101500000t" end="12124900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是初代怪异杀手的全名</font></p>
<p begin="12130900000t" end="12179100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长自然也是想弄清情敌的名字对吧</font></p>
<p begin="12252500000t" end="12274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不小心听到了你们的谈话</font></p>
<p begin="12275700000t" end="12285700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么又是你？</font></p>
<p begin="12282800000t" end="12290300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}放心吧。我已经避免了和她遭遇。</font></p>
<p begin="12290300000t" end="12297800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}她过去的时候，我就贴在天花板上跑开了。</font></p>
<p begin="12303800000t" end="12346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">鬼哥哥  你在面对她的时候也太松懈了  怎么什么话都说？</font></p>
<p begin="12348000000t" end="12376800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是吗？我倒是没这么觉得</font></p>
<p begin="12380600000t" end="12406000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">鬼哥哥觉得没问题的话那就没问题</font></p>
<p begin="12410200000t" end="12448100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我现在要去北白蛇神社  你要一起去吗？</font></p>
<p begin="12451500000t" end="12469400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？那是什么地方？</font></p>
<p begin="12473600000t" end="12509900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">别忘啊  你忘的事情也太多了吧</font></p>
<p begin="12514000000t" end="12539100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那可是你主人失踪的地方</font></p>
<p begin="12545900000t" end="12565800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我不想和鬼哥哥一大早去约会</font></p>
<p begin="12570300000t" end="12602900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过这么说来  我也想问你一件事</font></p>
<p begin="12606200000t" end="12614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么事？</font></p>
<p begin="12617500000t" end="12644600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">鬼哥哥  你变成吸血鬼很幸福吗？</font></p>
<p begin="12662900000t" end="12688800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">初代怪异杀手不是说过吗？</font></p>
<p begin="12696700000t" end="12744700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「鬼哥哥和忍老师在一起  对我又有什么益处呢？」</font></p>
<p begin="12752200000t" end="12807200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">结果鬼哥哥当时也没能说出这对他有什么好处</font></p>
<p begin="12809700000t" end="12829400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但这个想法到现在也没有变化吗？</font></p>
<p begin="12838900000t" end="12886100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「鬼哥哥和忍老师在一起  谁都不会得到幸福」</font></p>
<p begin="12886100000t" end="12897800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事到如今你是不是依然这么想？</font></p>
<p begin="12926500000t" end="12937000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事到如今我依然这么想</font></p>
<p begin="12954500000t" end="12987800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁都不会幸福  谁也无法变得幸福</font></p>
<p begin="12994100000t" end="13050400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只要我身为一个吸血鬼  只要我和忍在一起  就只会给别人带来麻烦</font></p>
<p begin="13058300000t" end="13085400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比起任何人  都更让忍变得不幸</font></p>
<p begin="13105900000t" end="13126700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这听起来好像是个借口</font></p>
<p begin="13143800000t" end="13167600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就好像「我不会变得幸福所以就饶了我吧」</font></p>
<p begin="13171800000t" end="13233900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「我不会想要去变得幸福  所以请原谅我  请放过我」一样</font></p>
<p begin="13239800000t" end="13291500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还像「我们已经这么不幸了  所以不要责怪我们  多可怜啊」一样</font></p>
<p begin="13308200000t" end="13375300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说鬼哥哥  莫非你把甘于不幸与不遇也当做是一种努力吗？</font></p>
<p begin="13392000000t" end="13426600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">人们一般把这种事叫做「无所事事」</font></p>
<p begin="13430400000t" end="13468700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不要觉得不幸就该被原谅  你应该去追求Happy End</font></p>
<p begin="13474600000t" end="13491700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要不要我再踩一次你的脸？</font></p>
<p begin="13510400000t" end="13532600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">斧乃木妹妹还真是严厉</font></p>
<p begin="13540100000t" end="13588400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">坚持于不幸是一种怠慢  不去追求幸福也是一种卑鄙</font></p>
<p begin="13595900000t" end="13625600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果这样的话  自杀的先驱者也就无法得到报答了</font></p>
<p begin="13636000000t" end="13646000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我暂且听了</font></p>
<p begin="13670200000t" end="13686500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁都没有变得幸福</font></p>
<p begin="13694800000t" end="13718800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">无论是我  还是小忍  还是任何一个人</font></p>
<p begin="13718800000t" end="13728800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}<font size="42">至少如今我是如此认为的</font></font></p>
<p begin="13728800000t" end="13738800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}<font size="42">事到如今我依然如此认为</font></font></p>
<p begin="13745300000t" end="13794500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而  说不定在很久以后  在很远的未来</font></p>
<p begin="13799100000t" end="13872100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比如说在四百年后  这个想法或许也会有些许变化  我如此想着</font></p>
<p begin="13879600000t" end="13933000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算不幸福  然而庆幸的是  我有多到烂掉的时间</font></p>
<p begin="13940300000t" end="13951100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只有时间</font></p>
<p begin="13955100000t" end="13988000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">无论是思考的时间  还是活着的时间  多到令人厌烦</font></p>
<p begin="13993800000t" end="14028000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">直到变为尸体而腐烂为止  我们还有许多时间</font></p>
<p begin="14044700000t" end="14104400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而  这些时间的逝去  或许也同样只是时间的问题</font></p>
<p begin="14222000000t" end="14281200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="14222000000t" end="14281200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="14281600000t" end="14342100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14281600000t" end="14342100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="14463500000t" end="14546100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">在教室窗子上呼气的水雾中写下的名字</font></p>
<p begin="14463500000t" end="14546100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}教室の窓に息を吐いて描いた名前</font></p>
<p begin="14546100000t" end="14576500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我慌忙地用袖子将它檫去</font></p>
<p begin="14546100000t" end="14576500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}もぅ慌てて袖で消した</font></p>
<p begin="14576500000t" end="14643700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那是因为走廊中传来了你的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14576500000t" end="14643700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}廊下から君の声がしたから</font></p>
<p begin="14643700000t" end="14715800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我假装毫不在意  早早地回了家</font></p>
<p begin="14643700000t" end="14715800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}心誤魔化すように早足で帰った</font></p>
<p begin="14715800000t" end="14799600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">不知从什么时候起我无法和你说话</font></p>
<p begin="14715800000t" end="14799600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何時からか私は君と話せなくなった</font></p>
<p begin="14800100000t" end="14859300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="14800100000t" end="14859300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="14859700000t" end="14916000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14859700000t" end="14916000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="14916000000t" end="14972300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">无须说出任何话语就可以注意到自己的人比什么都重要</font></p>
<p begin="14916000000t" end="14972300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何も言わなくたって すぐ気付いてくれた人</font></p>
<p begin="14972700000t" end="15042000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">即时此刻注意到这一点  然而我们已经无法再面对</font></p>
<p begin="14972700000t" end="15042000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何より大切と気付いても もう目も合わない</font></p>
